-// Patch 0012: prominent success/fail banners. Original feedback was a 12pt
-// dim yellow line at the bottom of a bottom-anchored panel — easily missed,
-// and worse, often hidden behind the level bar / loadout strip. Now: two
-// big colored banners (green/red) shown right under the panel title for
